org.matsim.analysis

Class ScoreStatsControlerListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.matsim.analysis.ScoreStatsControlerListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EventListener, ScoreStats, MatsimExtensionPoint, ControlerListener, IterationEndsListener, ShutdownListener, StartupListener

    public class ScoreStatsControlerListener
extends Object
implements StartupListener, IterationEndsListener, ShutdownListener, ScoreStats
    Calculates at the end of each iteration the following statistics:
    • average score of the selected plan
    • average of the score of the worst plan of each agent
    • average of the score of the best plan of each agent
    • average of the average score of all plans of each agent
    Plans with undefined scores are not included in the statistics. The calculated values are written to a file, each iteration on a separate line.
    Author:
    mrieser
